Add to Cmake of openCV:



-D PYTHON_EXECUTABLE=/usr/bin/python3.4/
-D PYTHON_INCLUDE=/usr/include/python3.4/
-D PYTHON_LIBRARY=/usr/lib/libpython3.4.a
-D PYTHON_PACKAGES_PATH=/usr/local/lib/python3.4/site-packages/
-D PYTHON_NUMPY_INCLUDE_DIR=/usr/local/lib/python3.4/dist-packages/numpy/core/include
